| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2001 — Recovery Inhibition (VanHelsing)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 105a286c-4d4f-5c24-840c-7b84c1cc4625"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
